.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing, handball, biathlon, soccer
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, satire, disaster, zombie, animation
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, may, august, april, december
House: palace, colonial, cottage, gothic-revival, cape-cod
There 5 different types of food: pomegranate, garlic, banana, carrot, avocado

1. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse
2. the person watching satire movies is the person eating pomegranate
3. the palace house is the person who's sport is surfing
4. the person watching disaster movies is the colonial house
5. the person who's sport is surfing is to the right of the person who's sport is handball
6. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating avocado
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's sport is biathlon
8. the cottage house is in the middle
9. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person eating garlic
11. the person who's birthday is in may is to the left or right of the person eating carrot
12. the person who's birthday is in april is the gothic-revival house
13. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in december
14. the person watching zombie movies is to the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Movie-Genre	|   zombie	|    disaster	|     scientific	|    satire	|    animation	|
| Sport		|    biathlon	|      soccer	|      lacrosse	|     handball	|     surfing	|
| House	|     cape-cod	|      colonial	|      cottage	| gothic-revival	|     palace	|
| Birthday		|     may	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| april	|   parliament	|
| Food		|     garlic	|     carrot	|     avocado	|     pomegranate	|     banana	|
